CatDescriptText: The signs hanging on the back wall read, "There Will Be A Small Increase In Prices Of All Drinks At 9:30 P.M." and "The Granville Hotel Presents, Key Boy and his Sharps and Flats In the Pine Room Every Thurs. Fri. Sat. Nites 10 - 3, Plus Reva George, Every Fri. and Sat...Every Thursday".
TitMainTitle: Comedian Kel-O-Kelly or Kelo Kelly, and Hosea Taylor (Jose Gonzales) on saxophone, performing at the Granville Hotel with man playing guitar in background
